::Shadow Wing::

"How many bots are in the Allience? Do we have the bot power to pull off 
such a mission right now? I know I shouldn't be thinking of revenge. It's 
wrong to want revenge.  But, I just don't want to lay down for them either.  
I want to do something." She looked down and sighed.  "I guess my logic 
ciruits are messed up or something.  I want to fight back and strike first 
for once. I know it's wrong, but want to taake them out before they take us 
out."

----Original Message---
From:   <Yanshosh@a...>
Date: Wed Jul 5, 2000 5:58pm
Subject: Re: Neo Beast Wars


::Prowl::

Prowl looks over at Shadow Wing as she flies up to him. He shruggs, a hard
thing to do while flying.

"The newcomer's base is closer than all the rest. They also stand in the way
of us and the preds. And the Alliance for that matter. With any luck, 
they'll
keep us safe without even knowing it."

Prowl frowns, thinking of something. "But they're the ones that did the most
damage to the Ark. Maybe we should attack them and try to take them out."
